    Mann, Ivanov and Ferber

    Mann, Ivanov and Ferber


    When we open a book, we become creators in an instant. By erasing the boundaries between the life of the author and our life, we create a work of art that is visible only to us.
    Reading is like jazz. It's impossible to go wrong here. This is where self-confidence comes into play. The ability to hear what resonates in the heart and what does not. In reading, we always remain ourselves. And always in contact with the world.
    Reading books means hearing the call of eternity and responding to it. To let in chaos, to open up to that part of yourself where everyone defines honesty and audacity. See the light behind the shadow. And fearlessly feel that we all live in a world that cannot be explained. But you can read.

    In May 2021, on the eve of our birthday, we played associations. And it turned out that if MYTH is a color, then white. As a combination of all colors of the spectrum. If MYTH is like sound, then it is the rustling of pages and the sounds of jazz. If MYTH is action, then flight. Up, to yourself, to the future.

    And MYTH is the way. Harmony. Light. Convenient working conditions. Creation. Adventure. Work. Wisdom. Community of like-minded people. Life in pleasure and the ability to be in the moment. Knowledge. Professionalism and support. Development technology. Courses and books. Slowing down time and expanding perception.

    MYTH is all those who read books and those who choose them. All those who take courses and those who create them. MYTH is a lot of names and surnames. MYTH is all of us.
